'''''All Alone''''' is a solo piano album by [[Dolo Coker]] which was recorded in 1979 and released on the [[Xanadu Records|Xanadu]] label in 1981.<ref>[http://www.jazzlists.com/SJ_Label_Xanadu.htm Xanadu Records discography] accessed April 30, 2014</ref><ref>Fitzgerald, M., [http://www.jazzdiscography.com/Leaders/CokerDolo-ldr.php Dolo Coker Leader Entry] accessed April 30, 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.jazzdisco.org/dolo-coker/catalog/#xanadu-139 Dolo Coker discography] accessed April 30, 2014</ref> 

==Reception==
{{Album ratings
| rev1 = [[AllMusic]]
| rev1Score = {{rating|3|5}}<ref name="Allmusic"/> 
}}
[[AllMusic]] reviewer Scott Yanow states, "Dolo Coker's fourth and final album as a leader is a set of unaccompanied piano solos with the emphasis on reflective ballads (although there are also a couple of swinging tunes)".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S., [http://www.allmusic.com/album/all-alone-mw0000876313 Allmusic Review] accessed April 30, 2014</ref>

